thread.title_full: Fast Cover Travel Insurance reviewed by Yvonne

author: Yvonne
title: Yvonne
text: Found this company on the internet along with several others. It offered the most competitive pricing. Had to buy on the free line as my husband and I are over 69. Great consultant, no hassle. Hopefully we don't have to make a claim, but would like to add to the review if this happens.
